WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.485 --> 00:00:01.460
Good morning family.

00:00:01.785 --> 00:00:05.071
I have some things on my heart today.

00:00:06.919 --> 00:00:11.316
As a prophetic intercessor, I see a lot.

00:00:11.948 --> 00:00:16.640
The Lord and I have a real tight relationship about a lot of things.

00:00:18.239 --> 00:00:37.640
I've noticed this because I try to let you all in on things, and I really feel it's important that you come up higher in your relationship with the Lord in 2024.

00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:39.200
Let's go higher.

00:00:39.200 --> 00:01:07.600
These are just conversations I have with the Lord, but it's really important that I get this across to you all because I see that people are starting to notice me on YouTube, in public, or when I'm talking to people on the phone.

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:18.720
When I'm watching videos of other people, people want to do collabs or have conversations with you.

00:01:24.449 --> 00:01:29.159
It's kind of like a dog at a park—I hate to say that—but when you see a little dog at the park, everyone is sniffing everyone.

00:01:29.159 --> 00:01:36.720
They are always trying to see who you are, wanting to know your business.

00:01:41.261 --> 00:01:41.972
I deal with dogs; it's just the way they are.

00:01:41.972 --> 00:01:47.960
They are always sniffing everything and want to know everybody's business.

00:01:47.960 --> 00:02:00.926
Dogs are friendly, but sometimes they are aggressive, and you have to be cautious about what kind of dog you are around.

00:02:00.926 --> 00:02:02.124
Just being real.

00:02:02.124 --> 00:02:14.262
I don't know if that was a bad illustration, but I'm going to go with it.

00:02:14.262 --> 00:02:26.799
When I'm on the phone, the Lord prophetically will tell me, 'He's lying to you' or 'She's lying to you.

00:02:26.799 --> 00:02:35.296
' He'll warn me, 'This person has this sin, and you need to be cautious of this,' especially if they want to do business with you.

00:02:38.410 --> 00:02:41.895
A lot of times He'll say, 'No, do not do business with that individual.

00:02:41.895 --> 00:02:53.394
' He'll reveal private things about that individual to me—not to gossip, but because He's warning me.

00:02:53.394 --> 00:02:57.690
We are tight; we have a relationship.

00:02:57.690 --> 00:03:11.068
It's like how you are able to talk to your spouse and tell them things you wouldn't tell anyone else because you are friends.

00:03:17.550 --> 00:03:28.680
I'm going to make this a two-part thing, but I don't want to touch too much on the friendship part of being a friend of God yet.

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:52.090
What I'm trying to say is whenever I'm on the phone with an individual or if I meet them in public and they want to get together for dinner, the Lord says, 'No.

00:03:52.090 --> 00:04:00.840
' They might get offended, but the Lord always tells me there's more to this than what I realize.

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:03.548
He's trying to protect me.

00:04:03.548 --> 00:04:12.160
Do you want Him to lead and guide you in everything you do or not?

00:04:12.160 --> 00:04:16.680
God has an opinion about everyone.

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:24.150
One time, I was really hurt by a pastor I had talked to before.

00:04:39.101 --> 00:04:49.146
The Lord came to me and apologized for how that individual treated me.

00:04:49.146 --> 00:05:03.262
He said, 'Brandon, I just want to let you know that was wrong, and I know your heart is hurt.

00:05:03.262 --> 00:05:10.035
' He said, 'I just want to apologize on behalf of them.

00:05:10.035 --> 00:05:21.560
' I said, 'Lord, they had a bad day, and people have things going on; I forgive them.

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:28.706
' We had a conversation, and I brought up another person.

00:05:28.706 --> 00:05:35.479
He said, 'Brandon, that person's heart is good before Me.

00:05:35.479 --> 00:05:43.314
They wouldn't have done that, and they wouldn't have treated you that way.

00:05:43.314 --> 00:05:47.219
I know that for a fact.

00:05:59.106 --> 00:06:06.100
If that person would have known your telephone number, they would have called you personally and never treated you that way.

00:06:06.100 --> 00:06:15.489
' It took me back because of the way God spoke so highly of this individual.

00:06:15.489 --> 00:06:19.039
It made me examine myself like a mirror.

00:06:19.039 --> 00:06:38.748
If I am able to see prophetically when I am standing before a person, God will reveal things about them—whether they have anger issues, lying issues, if they are greedy, or if their motive is not pure.

00:06:38.748 --> 00:06:45.486
Caution, caution, caution, or a go, go, go!

00:06:45.486 --> 00:06:50.211
He'll say, 'Yes, this person is good.

00:06:50.211 --> 00:06:53.373
Green means go, buddy!

00:06:53.373 --> 00:06:56.240
' Or: 'Red means stop!

00:06:56.240 --> 00:07:01.687
Don't do that, Brandon; they'll end up ripping you off.

00:07:01.687 --> 00:07:03.793
Stay away from them.

00:07:04.319 --> 00:07:18.795
You can go certain ways in certain areas with this relationship, but it does not ever go to this level.

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:30.730
Don't let them in your inner circle; they are a gossip and will backstab you.

00:07:30.730 --> 00:07:33.390
' He warns me of things.

00:07:33.390 --> 00:07:39.613
But my question to you is: what does God say about you?

00:07:39.613 --> 00:07:59.433
He sees into the depth of your heart—all the hidden sin, the things you think you can fool everyone else with in the natural world.

00:08:14.919 --> 00:08:26.260
You think you can fool your pastor, your spouse, or who you are dating, but you can't fool God.

00:08:26.260 --> 00:08:41.959
He sees the depth of who you are from the time you were created in your mother's womb to the day you die.

00:08:41.959 --> 00:08:44.235
Who are you before Him?

00:08:44.235 --> 00:09:00.800
Yes, we are under the blood and our sins are washed away, but there are character issues people don't want to take care of.

00:09:00.800 --> 00:09:12.000
Deep down inside, if you were to stand before a prophetic person, what would God warn them about you?

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:25.484
I quickly want to examine myself and say, 'God, if I'm standing before somebody with a prophetic gift, what do they see about me?

00:09:25.484 --> 00:09:37.014
' It's not that it matters what they think, but it matters what God is relaying to them to warn them.

00:09:39.646 --> 00:09:46.085
He might say, 'They have these issues; you don't want to do business with them.

00:09:46.085 --> 00:09:57.770
' I'll be walking down the aisle at Walmart, and the Lord will say, 'Get your children close to you now.

00:09:57.770 --> 00:10:06.220
That man is a predator; he has sexual bad things toward children.

00:10:06.220 --> 00:10:09.990
' It's a warning for protection.

00:10:09.990 --> 00:10:20.350
Don't let them go to that party because those kids' parents are loose in the way they raise their children.

00:10:20.350 --> 00:10:25.824
Don't allow them to go because they are a mixed bag.

00:10:27.991 --> 00:10:29.547
Does God have an opinion about you?

00:10:29.547 --> 00:10:31.440
Yes, He does.

00:10:31.440 --> 00:10:40.585
What things do you think you're hiding from people that you think you're fooling everybody else?

00:10:42.811 --> 00:10:43.025
God sees it.

00:10:47.818 --> 00:10:51.580
I want Him to look at me and say, 'He's perfect before Me.

00:10:51.580 --> 00:10:55.320
Well done, thou good and faithful servant.

00:10:55.320 --> 00:10:57.480
Brandon's a good one.

00:10:57.480 --> 00:11:03.239
' Do you see what I'm trying to say?

00:11:03.239 --> 00:11:06.870
What does God say about you?

00:11:14.904 --> 00:11:19.445
I wanted to come on today and tell you to examine your heart.

00:11:19.445 --> 00:11:27.440
It's not about gossip or trying to backbite; He always protects those He loves.

00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:46.188
He loves all His children, but when you have a covenant with God—whenever you're a tither and a giver—what's mine is His and what's His is mine.

00:11:46.188 --> 00:11:53.399
If He tells me to pray right now, will I do it?

00:11:53.399 --> 00:12:01.406
If He tells you to give, would you give?

00:12:01.406 --> 00:12:14.488
If He tells you to sow $1,000, would you be quick to do it because you are obedient?

00:12:20.360 --> 00:12:20.800
He examines your heart.

00:12:20.800 --> 00:12:36.759
If He says go and pray for that person right now because they are hurting and wanting to hurt themselves physically, would you obey Him?

00:12:36.759 --> 00:12:41.100
Are you quick to do these things?

00:12:41.100 --> 00:12:47.538
Are you a gossip, a complainer, or a backbiter?

00:12:55.856 --> 00:12:56.199
Do you talk bad about people and ridicule them?

00:12:56.199 --> 00:13:01.930
Are you abusive verbally to your children or spouse?

00:13:02.700 --> 00:13:14.344
Do you treat them like trash on the way to church and then act all holy and sanctimonious?

00:13:14.344 --> 00:13:23.764
Then you get back in the car and fuss all the way home, cussing them out.

00:13:23.764 --> 00:13:26.520
Does God look at you?

00:13:26.520 --> 00:13:30.800
When you get real with God, God will get real with you.

00:13:30.800 --> 00:13:36.120
He sees even when you're angry at Him.

00:13:39.440 --> 00:13:45.325
I go before God, and He knows if I'm ticked off or having a bad day.

00:13:49.460 --> 00:13:49.688
I don't hide it.

00:13:50.372 --> 00:13:52.940
I say, 'Lord, I'm having a rough day.

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:59.456
The pressure from the demonic or whatever is going on, and I need some spiritual backing here.

00:13:59.456 --> 00:14:01.017
Where are You at?

00:14:01.017 --> 00:14:07.160
' He'll say, 'You haven't spent enough time in prayer today, Brandon.

00:14:07.160 --> 00:14:12.790
' It's always me; I'm the one at fault, never God.

00:14:12.790 --> 00:14:15.706
I'm the one with the issue.

00:14:26.795 --> 00:14:27.120
He's perfect, but I want to be an open book.

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:28.046
Change me.

00:14:28.046 --> 00:14:32.764
Create in me a clean heart, O God.

00:14:32.764 --> 00:14:38.319
Search me, know me, and mold me into who I need to be.

00:14:50.375 --> 00:14:50.863
I hope this is coming across as important because I want you to know how much Jesus loves you.

00:14:50.863 --> 00:14:59.298
It needs to be more than just a love; it needs to be an intimacy.

00:14:59.298 --> 00:15:03.177
What does He say about you?

00:15:03.177 --> 00:15:07.040
What is His heart toward you?

00:15:26.520 --> 00:15:27.000
I keep saying it over and over again because I want to drive it home.

00:15:41.519 --> 00:15:41.799
It's so important.

00:15:42.079 --> 00:15:53.810
When He lets me examine a person in the spirit and warns me about them, I know it can be reversed.

00:15:53.810 --> 00:15:56.697
What do they see about me?

00:15:56.697 --> 00:16:09.290
I know I'm not perfect, and my family isn't perfect, but we are quick to repent.

00:16:09.290 --> 00:16:13.639
We are quick to take communion and fall at His feet.

00:16:13.639 --> 00:16:29.219
Father, I need You in my business dealings, when I'm trying to do a car deal or flip something on eBay.

00:16:29.219 --> 00:16:34.289
Show me the secret things that nobody else can see.

00:16:34.289 --> 00:16:43.720
Part of my gifting is that He reveals hidden things to me about investments.

00:16:43.720 --> 00:16:49.776
I'm no special person; I'm a work in progress.

00:16:59.639 --> 00:17:01.399
But I ask Him to help me not lose His money because it's His money; I'm just a steward.

00:17:08.540 --> 00:17:16.306
I don't want to bury it in the dirt; I want to invest it and be faithful with a little so He'll make me ruler over much.

00:17:16.306 --> 00:17:25.706
He'll show me investments, and if people try to take advantage of me, the Lord warns me.

00:17:27.453 --> 00:17:31.377
I always go with the love of God, knowing what He warned me about.

00:17:31.377 --> 00:17:36.284
They don't know that I know what they know.

00:17:36.284 --> 00:17:41.290
He'll show me investments and highlight them.

00:17:41.290 --> 00:17:48.338
Sometimes I'll say, 'This one is going to be good,' and it's just conversation.

00:17:48.338 --> 00:17:52.303
Someone once asked if I invested in those things.

00:17:52.303 --> 00:17:57.960
No, because I'm not after greed; it's about the relationship.

00:18:00.060 --> 00:18:03.902
I want to know every secret thing He has.

00:18:05.004 --> 00:18:16.420
I want to lay my head upon His chest and know His breath when He exhales and inhales.

00:18:16.420 --> 00:18:20.800
I want to know everything about Him.

00:18:20.800 --> 00:18:25.120
The Holy Spirit has a fragrance—every single thing about Him.

00:18:25.120 --> 00:18:31.133
When He's having a hard day with His kids, I can feel it.

00:18:33.911 --> 00:18:34.436
I asked, 'Father, are You okay today?

00:18:34.436 --> 00:18:39.816
' He said, 'Brandon, my children were very disobedient today.

00:18:39.816 --> 00:18:45.120
' I could feel He was agitated.

00:18:45.120 --> 00:18:50.679
When you get to know somebody, you know when they are agitated.

00:19:01.867 --> 00:19:02.133
I don't want to be super religious, but He shows me colors.

00:19:02.133 --> 00:19:07.580
Colors are big in the spirit realm.

00:19:07.580 --> 00:19:17.731
When you get close to God, He shows you big secret things.

00:19:36.560 --> 00:19:37.000
I see colors around things as warnings—blacks, purples, pinks.

00:19:49.000 --> 00:19:49.440
I know it's stuff they are dealing with; they are prayer cues.

00:19:49.440 --> 00:19:51.880
It's about atmospheres.

00:19:51.880 --> 00:20:04.733
I can go into a church, and the Lord will warn me about what's going on with the pastor.

00:20:04.733 --> 00:20:09.373
He'll say, 'Don't go to church here.

00:20:12.679 --> 00:20:13.110
You need to get out quick.

00:20:13.110 --> 00:20:17.384
Don't trust them about spiritual giftings.

00:20:17.384 --> 00:20:22.491
' The pastor might be jealous and want competition.

00:20:22.491 --> 00:20:25.178
He'll warn me about atmospheres.

00:20:25.178 --> 00:20:28.440
I'm very sensitive to them.

00:20:28.440 --> 00:20:42.880
People ask to go out to dinner, but I don't go because I protect the gift inside of me.

00:21:01.779 --> 00:21:02.149
I don't go out flippantly.

00:21:02.149 --> 00:21:13.726
At Christmas, my family wanted me to go over, but I stayed with my wife and kids.

00:21:13.726 --> 00:21:31.775
It's not that I'm better; I'm just very sensitive to atmospheres and watchful over where I put myself.

00:21:43.738 --> 00:21:43.956
I don't just go get coffee with people unless I have an inkling the Holy Spirit says to do it.

00:21:43.956 --> 00:21:47.800
I'm an intercessor; I seek His face.

00:21:47.800 --> 00:21:53.799
My safe place is my children and my wife.

00:22:01.875 --> 00:22:04.594
I don't want to be rude, but 99% of the time, I'm going to say no.

00:22:11.024 --> 00:22:11.369
I just wanted to let you know me more.

00:22:11.369 --> 00:22:12.060
I hope that blessed you.

00:22:12.060 --> 00:22:14.611
It's important to the Father.

00:22:14.611 --> 00:22:24.080
If you want to come up higher, you'll work on this stuff.

00:22:24.080 --> 00:22:29.190
Let me pray for you.

00:22:29.190 --> 00:22:37.576
Father, I thank You for every single person represented here.

00:22:37.576 --> 00:22:42.789
May they come up higher in their relationship with You.

00:22:42.789 --> 00:22:53.222
It's all about falling in love with Jesus and having intimacy with the Holy Spirit.

00:22:53.222 --> 00:23:02.940
Ultimately, it's about falling in love more with Jesus on a day-to-day basis.

00:23:16.085 --> 00:23:21.045
I thank You that every person watching this would have the opportunity to come up higher—to hear Your voice and smell the fragrance of who You are.

00:23:29.475 --> 00:23:29.743
I bless them in the name of Jesus.

00:23:29.743 --> 00:23:35.840
May this message inspire them to grow and become more intimate with You.

00:23:35.840 --> 00:23:38.255
Create in them a clean heart.

00:23:38.255 --> 00:23:43.919
Help them turn further from the world and closer to Jesus.

00:23:43.919 --> 00:23:52.240
It is about knowing what You did for us on that cross.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
I thank You that they are healed and whole because Christ redeemed us from the curse of the law.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
I call healing and wholeness over every person right now in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
Delivered from satanic bondage, they are no longer bound.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
For whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
You've set us free from sickness, poverty, and lack.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
You bore it all on the cross.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Thank You for Your intimacy.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We are coming up higher every day, going from glory to glory.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
We give You praise, glory, and honor.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Amen.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
I appreciate you watching.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Please click that like button and subscribe if you aren't already.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Click the notification bell.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
I would really appreciate it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
We are getting the gospel out throughout the whole world every time you do that—commenting nicely and sharing.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
We are getting people born again, and that's what it's all about—getting people to know Jesus and be intimate with Him.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Thank you; you've meant a lot to me and my family.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We will see you next time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Have a blessed day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
